<plot>A story of a decision. There is a story. The protagonists - the writer and his wife - have to decide whether to keep a fourth child that is on the way. There is a hero or rather a heroine who is Anna, the wife. So, we see a married couple, deeply devoted to each other and a very serious conflict "... to give birth here would be a tragedy. No, worse, a comedy..." There are already three children and whether to have the fourth, that is the question.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?041469</url></doc>
